<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>이 책은 다음과 같이 구성이 되어 있습니다.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>파트1] 네이버 블로그 제대로 준비해서 시작하기</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>파트2] 방문자를 사로잡는 블로그 콘텐츠 작성하기</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>파트3] 네이버 블로그 마케팅의 핵심, 검색 상위 노출</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>파트4] 나만의 특색있는 블로그 만들고 꾸미기</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>파트5] 스마트에디터 ONE 활용해 톡톡 튀는 콘텐츠 작성하기</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>이 책에서는 마케팅의 핵심,검색상위 노출 방법까지 하나하나 쉽게 설명을 해 주고 있는데요.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>이 책의 내용을 한번 살펴 보겠습니다.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: "Noto Sans Demilight", "Noto Sans KR"; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1a5490; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important'>파트1]&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: "Noto Sans Demilight", "Noto Sans KR"; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1a5490; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important'><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">네이버 블로그 제대로 준비해서 시작하기</span>&nbsp;</span>편에서는</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">어떤 블로그를 만들것인지 계획하고 시작하는 방법에 대해 알려 주고 있습니다.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">네이버에 활성화 되어 있는 블로그는 1000만개 이상이고 지금도 수많은 블로그가 개설되고 있습니다.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">그렇다면 차별성 없는 블로그는 사람들의 시선을 사로잡기 힘들것입니다.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">그렇다면 어떻게 차별성을 둘것인지에 대해 알아 보시죠.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: "Noto Sans Demilight", "Noto Sans KR"; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1a5490; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important'><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">파트2] 방문자를 사로잡는 블로그 콘텐츠 작성하기</span></span>&nbsp;편에서는</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>네이버 블로그는 누구나 시작할 수 있지만 누구나 잘 할 수는 없습니다.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>블로그를 잘하기 위해서는 먼저 어떤 블로그를 만들지 주제가 정확해야 합니다. 여행,취미,맛집,일상생활 등 정확한 주제를 정하고 45일~60일간 매일 1일 1개 이상의 포스팅을 해 준다면 최적화가 됩니다.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>이렇게 최적화 된 블로그는 다음과 같은 C-Rank 알고리즘과 DIA 모델에 근거해서 검색 상위 노출이 되게 되는데요.&nbsp;</p>
