<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>검색엔진 최적화 방법의 다양한 방법들에 대한 설명을 통해 검색상위노출 방법에 대해 설명이 되어 있는데요.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>그 중 하나는 키워드를 활용해서 방문자 늘리기 방법등이 있을 수 있습니다.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>키워드도구는 네이버광고의 신규가입을 통해서 확인해 볼 수 있는데요.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>이러한 키워드 도구에서 제공하는 사용자통계 등을 이용하여 자신이 사용할 키워드를 확인해 볼 수도 있습니다.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>또한 네이버 데이터랩을 통해서 검색어 트랜드 등을 확인해 볼 수가 있으므로 이러한 도구를 이용해서도 적절한 포스팅을 한다면 효과가 증가 할 수 있겠네요.</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: "Noto Sans Demilight", "Noto Sans KR"; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1a5490; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important'><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">파트4] 나만의 특색있는 블로그 만들고 꾸미기</span>&nbsp;</span>편에서는 방문자의 시선을 사로잡을 수 있는 잘 갖춰진 블로그를 만드는 노하우를 설명하고 있습니다.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">타이틀 이미지 직접 등록 방법이나 내 블로그에 맞는 레이아웃 찾기,위젯 설정하기 등 자신만의 블로그를 만드는 방법을 통해서 자신만의 블로그를 만들 수 있습니다.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: "Noto Sans Demilight", "Noto Sans KR"; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1a5490; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important'><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">파트5] 스마트에디터 ONE 활용해 톡톡 튀는 콘텐츠 작성하기</span></span>&nbsp;편에서는 마지막으로 네이버의 에디터에서 제공해주는 기능들을 이용해서 톡톡 튀는 컨텐츠를 만들 수 있다는 점.</span>
</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>&nbsp;</p>
<p style='box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: Lato, entypo, "맑은 고딕", "malgun gothic", AppleGothicNeoSD, "Apple SD 산돌고딕 Neo", sans-serif; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.625em; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.3px; background-color: #ffffff; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important'>
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; -webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased !important">혹시라도 블로그를 만드는 것이 두렵거나 지금 시작하려고 하시는 분들이 이 책을 읽어 보신다면 정말 많은 도움이 되지 않을까 생각해 보네요.</span>
</p></p>  
